, critical race studies, and American studies"--cProvided by publisher.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aAfrican American theaterxHistoryy20th century. 0aAfrican AmericansxRace identity. 0aWhitesxRace identity. 0aAfrican Americans in the performing arts. 0aUnited StatesxRace relationsy20th century. 4aElectronic books.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher. 0aTheater--text/theory/performance.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.5262413